# =============================================================================
# KhataBox — Consolidated Environment References
# =============================================================================
# This file is a pointer only. Environment variable examples live in:
#
#   .env.example                    — Master consolidated (all vars, root)
#   frontend/.env.example           — Next.js frontend only
#   backend/.env                    — FastAPI backend (actual .env)
#   config/.env.example.backend     — FastAPI template (legacy)
#   config/.env.example.frontend    — Next.js template (legacy)
#
# How to set up:
#   1. cp .env.example            .env              (optional — root reference)
#   2. cp frontend/.env.example   frontend/.env     (frontend vars)
#   3. cp config/.env.example.backend  backend/.env (already exists)
#
# NEVER commit actual .env files. They are gitignored.
